data.description: Why wait for a home to be constructed when you can move into one that's ready now? This 2023 build is the answer to your desires, offering 4 bedrooms and 2.5 baths. The house boasts luxurious LVP flooring throughout the first floor and impressive 9' ceilings. The upgraded kitchen is a culinary haven, featuring white cabinetry, granite countertops, a stylish tile backsplash, and new appliances.  This property goes beyond with a gas fireplace, perfect for chilly weather, second-floor laundry, and a beautiful master suite with a private bath, among other features. The yard displays a stamped patio that was an additional piece for entertainment.  Don't miss out—plan your visit today. Conveniently located near major commuter routes and amenities, this home is ready for you. Schedule your tour now and step into your dream home!
